ARTICLE.TITLE: Nigerian Lady Tests Positive For Coronavirus In Lagos
ARTICLE.TEXT:
The Federal Ministry of Health has confirmed the third case of the novel Coronavirus, COVID19, in Nigeria.

This was announced on the official Twitter page of the Nigeria Centre for Disease Control.

The tweet reads;

“The Honourable Minister @Fmohnigeria has announced the 3rd case of #COVID19 in Nigeria

“The case is a Nigerian who returned to Lagos from UK & developed symptoms during her 14-day self-isolation

“She is clinically stable & is being treated at Infectious Disease Hospital, Lagos“
